  "content": {
    "prompt": "Write a program that generates the output as below. Use only variables in the print-statements, so `print(\"text\")` is not allowed but `print(a)` or `print(a,z,a)` is allowed.\n\nRequired output:\n<pre style=\"margin-left:0mm\">\nDetroit cows that\nDetroit cows bully ,\nbully Detroit cows\nBuffalo buffalo Buffalo buffalo buffalo buffalo Buffalo buffalo\n</pre>",
    "source_code": "a = \"Detroit\"\r\nb = \"cows\"\r\nc = \"that\"\r\nd = \"bully\"\r\ne = \",\"\r\nf = \"Buffalo\"\r\ng = \"buffalo\"\r\nprint(a,b,c)\r\nprint(a,b,d,e)\r\nprint(d,a,b)\r\nprint(f,g,f,g,g,g,f,g)"
  },
